<a href="https://andscape.com/features/hall-of-fame-jerry-west-designer-alan-siegel-nba-logo/">andscape.com</a></p></section></div><div class="section-pb"><div class="container Contact_container__P1AUc"><div class="Contact_preview__KkYQG"><div class="Contact_contact_image__mhpBE"><img alt="nba-logo-vector-4e4e4e" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="//images.ctfassets.net/h8q6lxmb5akt/6ZIqXTrg5oY66TeSNfPJvl/688d980547989a572d2aef19be8a9887/nba-logo-vector-4e4e4e.svg"/></div></div><div class="stage-small">START YOUR JOURNEY WITH ANDY, EXPERIENCE CONSULTANT</div><h2 class="h2 Contact_title__kILC8"> <!-- -->Let’s work together<!-- --> </h2><div class="Contact_text__NDgW4">Looking for a logo designer? Enter your email below and we will contact you to see if we&#x27;re the right fit.</div><form class="ContactField_form__N23Uw Contact_subscription__Y4Ra3" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" noValidate="" action="https://andyedge.us1.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=be177a5c81f1b242ee4865dfa&amp;amp;id=a22dd548c0&amp;amp;f_id=00b874e2f0" method="post" target="_blank"><div id="mc-field-group"><input class="ContactField_input__zDVOb" type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required="" name="EMAIL" value=""/><button class="ContactField_btn__TccW3" aria-label="Submit email subscription" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" type="submit" name="subscribe"><svg class="" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M10.39 3.153c.464-.428 1.187-.399 1.615.065l3.692 4c.404.438.404 1.113 0 1.55l-3.692 4c-.428.464-1.151.493-1.615.065s-.493-1.151-.065-1.615l1.922-2.082H1.143C.512 9.136 0 8.624 0 7.993S.512 6.85 1.143 6.85h11.104l-1.922-2.082c-.428-.464-.399-1.187.065-1.615z"></path></svg></button></div><div id="mce-responses" class="ContactField_response___nvMF"><div class="response" id="mce-error-response" style="display:none"></div><div clas